initialize argparser

setup_default_argparser.Rd

Setup default argparser

Usage

setup_default_argparser(description = "", default_output = "output")

Arguments

description

Description for script

output_default

Default output directory

Value

parser object

Details

Set up a default argument parser, with two default arguments: log_level and output_dir

Examples

if (FALSE) { # \dontrun{
setup_default_argparser(description = "Example")
} # }
